cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.ST, cs.NA 

The paper proposes filtering and smoothing algorithms for state-space models with skew-t-distributed measurement noise. This topic is related to machine learning and statistical inference (cs.LG), control systems (cs.SY), information theory (cs.IT), statistics (cs.ST), and numerical analysis (cs.NA). The paper also presents simulations and tests based on real-world navigation data, which further supports the relevance of cs.LG and cs.SY. Therefore, cs.LG and cs.SY are the most likely categories, followed by cs.IT, cs.ST, and cs.NA.
